                    <h2 id="payment-request-GETapi-po-advance-request--po_id-">Get PO Advance Request Data (Prefill)</h2>

<p>
<small class="badge badge-darkred">requires authentication</small>
</p>

<p>Returns PO details with calculated amounts for PO advance request creation.
This replicates the logic from PurchaseOrderController@advanceRequestModal.</p>

<span id="example-requests-GETapi-po-advance-request--po_id-">
<blockquote>Example request:</blockquote>


<div class="bash-example">
    <pre><code class="language-bash">curl --request GET \
    --get "http://sitepilot/api/po-advance-request/16?workspace_id=16&amp;site_id=16" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"</code></pre></div>


<div class="javascript-example">
    <pre><code class="language-javascript">const url = new URL(
    "http://sitepilot/api/po-advance-request/16"
);

const params = {
    "workspace_id": "16",
    "site_id": "16",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key =&gt; url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};


fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response =&gt; response.json());</code></pre></div>

